v0.0.1

1 Iron Ingot + 2 Iron Nugget = 1 (original) -> 2 Chain
Repairment items of Chainmail armors changed: Iron Ingot -> Chain
Added Chainmail Horse Armor, can be crafted with 7 Chain
Added craft recipes for Chainmail armors: use chains to craft them
Added Netherite Horse Armor, will never natural generated from world, but can be upgraded from Diamond Horse Armor
Added Potential enchantment (for Trident), not compatible with Impaling, other just like Sharpness
Added Potion of Decay/Resistance, which need to brew with Wither Skull/Golden Apple
Added craft recipe for Enchanted Golden Apple: 8 Gold Blocks and 1 Apple
Added Charcoal Block, can be crafted or vice-versa with 9 Charcoal